OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Frather cloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with hill fog likely. Cloud
OL,8,Fthick enough to bring a few outbreaks
OL,9,Fof light rain and drizzle at times.
OL,10,FMild and feeling muggy for some in the
OL,11,Fsouth.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FAnother cloudy start to the
OL,14,Fday with some brightness developing in
OL,15,Fthe southeast later where it will feel
OL,16,Fwarm. Outbreaks of rain continuing for
OL,17,Fnorthern and western areas. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
